---
// Premium, highly styled HerWAY Forward Project Showcase
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>HerWAY Forward Project | Impact Showcase</title>
		<meta name="description" content="An impact showcase of the HerWAY Forward Project, which empowered first-time teenage mothers in Gasabo District, Rwanda." />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,600;0,700;0,800;1,600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	</head>
	<body class="bg-[#FCFAF6] text-slate-800 font-sans antialiased min-h-screen flex flex-col selection:bg-amber-100">
		
		<!-- Elegant Sticky Navigation Header -->
		<header class="bg-[#FCFAF6]/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-amber-100/20 py-5 sticky top-0 z-50 transition-all">
			<nav class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 flex justify-between items-center">
				<div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
					<div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-tr from-amber-400 via-emerald-500 to-sky-400 flex items-center justify-center shadow-md shadow-emerald-100">
						<span class="text-white font-extrabold text-sm tracking-tight">HWF</span>
					</div>
					<span class="font-extrabold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-900 to-emerald-700 tracking-tight text-lg">HerWAY Forward Project</span>
				</div>
				<div class="space-x-6 text-sm font-bold text-emerald-800">
					<a href="/" class="hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors relative after:content-[''] after:absolute after:bottom-[-4px] after:left-0 after:w-full after:h-[2px] after:bg-emerald-600">Home</a>
				</div>
			</nav>
		</header>
		
		<main class="flex-grow max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-16 w-full space-y-24">
			
			<!-- Gorgeous Hero Banner with Warm Sunset Glow -->
			<section class="relative p-8 md:p-16 rounded-[2rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50/70 via-emerald-50/40 to-sky-50/50 border border-amber-100/60 overflow-hidden shadow-lg shadow-amber-50/20">
				<!-- Abstract Glowing Background Orbs -->
				<div class="absolute -right-20 -top-20 w-64 h-64 bg-amber-300/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
				<div class="absolute -left-20 -bottom-20 w-64 h-64 bg-emerald-300/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
				
				<div class="relative space-y-8 max-w-3xl">
					<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
						<span class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-amber-800 bg-amber-100/70 border border-amber-200/50 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-sm">
							✓ Completed Peace Work
						</span>
						<span class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-emerald-800 bg-emerald-100/70 border border-emerald-200/50 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-sm">
							Gasabo District, Rwanda
						</span>
					</div>
					
					<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6.5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 leading-[1.05] font-serif">
						Reclaiming Dreams. <br />
						<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 via-amber-500 to-sky-500">Moving HerWAY Forward.</span>
					</h1>
					
					<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-light max-w-2xl">
						A look back at how we empowered first-time teenage mothers (ages 15–19) in Rwanda to reclaim their education, master vital life skills, and build self-determined, independent futures[cite: 1].
					</p>

					<div class="pt-6 flex items-center space-x-4 border-t border-slate-200/60">
						<div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-emerald-800 to-emerald-700 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm shadow-md">
							SU
						</div>
						<div>
							<div class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800">Led by Sandrine Uwantege</div>
							<div class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-medium">Washington and Lee University | Davis Projects for Peace Fellow[cite: 1]</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Beautiful Floating Mission & Vision Blocks -->
			<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
				<!-- Mission Block (Emerald Green Theme) -->
				<div class="relative bg-gradient-to-tr from-emerald-950 to-emerald-900 text-emerald-50 p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl shadow-emerald-950/10 overflow-hidden group hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
					<div class="absolute -right-6 -bottom-6 w-32 h-32 bg-emerald-800/20 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>
					<div class="mb-6 inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-emerald-800/40 text-emerald-300">
						<!-- Target/Impact Icon -->
						<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-emerald-300 mb-3">The Mission We Delivered</h3>
					<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed font-light text-emerald-100">
						We successfully empowered first-time teenage mothers in Rwanda to reclaim their education, realize their potential, and build confident, independent futures through personalized planning and communities of support[cite: 1].
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Vision Block (Amber Sunset Theme) -->
				<div class="relative bg-gradient-to-tr from-amber-600 to-amber-500 text-amber-50 p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl shadow-amber-600/10 overflow-hidden group hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
					<div class="absolute -right-6 -bottom-6 w-32 h-32 bg-amber-400/20 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>
					<div class="mb-6 inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl bg-amber-400/30 text-amber-100">
						<!-- Sunrise Icon -->
						<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364-6.364l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707m12.728 0l-.707-.707M6.343 6.364l-.707-.707M12 5a7 7 0 100 14 7 7 0 000-14z"></path></svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-amber-100 mb-3">Our Lasting Vision</h3>
					<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed font-light text-amber-50">
						A Rwanda where early pregnancy no longer ends a young woman's dreams, and where every teenage mother is met with a pathway to education, health, and financial independence[cite: 1].
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Activities Completed - Visual Showcase Grid -->
			<section class="space-y-12">
				<div class="text-center max-w-xl mx-auto space-y-3">
					<span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-emerald-700 bg-emerald-50 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full">Core Actions</span>
					<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 font-serif">Activities Completed</h2>
					<p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">The practical, community-centered pillars of our execution[cite: 1].</p>
				</div>

				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
					<!-- Card 1 -->
					<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-emerald-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden group flex flex-col">
						<div class="h-44 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/10 to-teal-500/5 flex items-center justify-center relative">
							<div class="h-16 w-16 rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-md flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-600 font-bold text-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">01</div>
							<div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 text-[10px] font-bold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full uppercase">Step 1</div>
						</div>
						<div class="p-8 flex-grow space-y-4">
							<h3 class="font-extrabold text-slate-900 text-lg leading-tight">Individualized Empowerment Plans</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
								Every participant partnered with a mentor to design her own personalized roadmap[cite: 1]. Together, they assessed educational backgrounds and interests to decide the best individual paths forward[cite: 1].
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Card 2 -->
					<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-amber-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden group flex flex-col">
						<div class="h-44 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500/10 to-orange-500/5 flex items-center justify-center relative">
							<div class="h-16 w-16 rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-md flex items-center justify-center text-amber-600 font-bold text-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">02</div>
							<div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 text-[10px] font-bold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full uppercase">Step 2</div>
						</div>
						<div class="p-8 flex-grow space-y-4">
							<h3 class="font-extrabold text-slate-900 text-lg leading-tight">Vocational & Inspiration Workshops</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
								We hosted tailoring workshops and practical skills sessions[cite: 1]. We invited inspirational guest speakers—former teenage mothers who built successful lives—to motivate and build self-sufficiency[cite: 1].
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Card 3 -->
					<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-sky-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden group flex flex-col">
						<div class="h-44 bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-500/10 to-indigo-500/5 flex items-center justify-center relative">
							<div class="h-16 w-16 rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-md flex items-center justify-center text-sky-600 font-bold text-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">03</div>
							<div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-sky-100 text-sky-800 text-[10px] font-bold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full uppercase">Step 3</div>
						</div>
						<div class="p-8 flex-grow space-y-4">
							<h3 class="font-extrabold text-slate-900 text-lg leading-tight">SRHR & Financial Literacy</h3>
							<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
								Participants completed age-appropriate reproductive health education to protect their bodies[cite: 1]. They also learned to budget, save, and formed peer-led saving groups to build collaborative financial independence[cite: 1].
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Editorial Styled Image Showcase (Deep Forest Green Frame) -->
			<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0c2a1c] to-[#061810] text-[#d4f2e3] rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 md:p-16 relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
				<div class="absolute right-0 top-0 w-1/3 h-full opacity-10 bg-[radial-gradient(#fff_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:20px_20px]"></div>
				
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12 items-center relative z-10">
					<div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">
						<span class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-emerald-350 bg-emerald-950/60 border border-emerald-800/40 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full">Project Gallery</span>
						<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold font-serif text-white leading-tight">Moments from Gasabo District</h2>
						<p class="text-emerald-100/70 leading-relaxed font-light text-sm">
							A look inside our weekly peer savings circles, tailored workshops, and mentor check-ins[cite: 1]. Add your real photos to the project easily by dropping them into your folder and updating the source links[cite: 1]!
						</p>
					</div>
					
					<!-- Highly Aesthetic Floating Image Display -->
					<div class="lg:col-span-3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
						<div class="h-44 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-900/30 border border-emerald-800/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-emerald-300/50 font-medium relative group overflow-hidden shadow-md">
							<!-- <img src="/images/gallery-1.jpg" alt="Mentorship session" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" /> -->
							<span class="relative z-10">[ Workshop Session Photo ]</span>
						</div>
						<div class="h-44 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-900/30 border border-emerald-800/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-emerald-300/50 font-medium relative group overflow-hidden shadow-md">
							<!-- <img src="/images/gallery-2.jpg" alt="Saving groups meeting" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" /> -->
							<span class="relative z-10">[ Saving Groups Photo ]</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Project Outcomes & Analytics (Bold Stats Page Layout) -->
			<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-16 border-t border-slate-200/60 pt-16">
				<div class="md:col-span-1 space-y-4">
					<span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-amber-700 bg-amber-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Deliverables</span>
					<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 font-serif">Project Outcomes</h2>
					<p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Our community-driven model produced direct, verifiable results for first-time teenage mothers[cite: 1].</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-8">
					<!-- Stunning Stat Badges -->
					<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
						<div class="bg-emerald-50/50 border border-emerald-100/30 p-8 rounded-3xl text-center space-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
							<div class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-emerald-700 font-serif">20</div>
							<div class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500">Young Mothers Empowered[cite: 1]</div>
						</div>
						<div class="bg-amber-50/50 border border-amber-100/30 p-8 rounded-3xl text-center space-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
							<div class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-amber-600 font-serif">10</div>
							<div class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500">Dedicated Mentors[cite: 1]</div>
						</div>
						<div class="bg-sky-50/50 border border-sky-100/30 p-8 rounded-3xl text-center space-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
							<div class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-sky-600 font-serif">100%</div>
							<div class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500">Actionable IEP Plans[cite: 1]</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Details Grid with Soft Checkmarks -->
					<div class="bg-[#F6F8F5] p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200/20 shadow-inner">
						<h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">Lasting Accomplishments</h4>
						<ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-sm text-slate-700">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<div class="h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-emerald-100/80 text-emerald-800 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 font-bold">✔</div>
								<div>
									<strong class="text-slate-900 block font-bold mb-0.5">Educational Clarity</strong>
									Defined plans to rejoin formal school or begin professional vocational trades[cite: 1].
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<div class="h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-emerald-100/80 text-emerald-800 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 font-bold">✔</div>
								<div>
									<strong class="text-slate-900 block font-bold mb-0.5">Informed Health</strong>
									Improved reproductive rights literacy, lowering repeat pregnancy risks[cite: 1].
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<div class="h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-emerald-100/80 text-emerald-800 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 font-bold">✔</div>
								<div>
									<strong class="text-slate-900 block font-bold mb-0.5">Financial Independence</strong>
									Savings habits fostered through ongoing peer savings circles[cite: 1].
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<div class="h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-emerald-100/80 text-emerald-800 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 font-bold">✔</div>
								<div>
									<strong class="text-slate-900 block font-bold mb-0.5">Stigma Reduced</strong>
									Emotional isolation replaced with a thriving, permanent peer support network[cite: 1].
								</div>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

		</main>

		<!-- Footer with Dark Emerald Theme -->
		<footer class="bg-[#091D13] text-white py-16 text-center mt-24">
			<div class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-4">
				<div class="text-md font-extrabold tracking-widest uppercase text-amber-400 font-serif">
					HerWAY Forward Project
				</div>
				<p class="text-xs text-emerald-100/70 leading-relaxed font-light">
					Reclaiming dreams. Building confidence. Transforming futures. A community-supported project for teenage mothers in Gasabo District, Rwanda[cite: 1].
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="text-[10px] text-emerald-100/40 border-t border-emerald-950 pt-8 mt-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} HerWAY Forward Project. Supported by the Davis Projects for Peace Fellowship[cite: 1].
			</div>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>